                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18130113-96-off566 t18130113-96-cd567"></join>, seven wire drawing plates, value 3 l. and three copper rings, value 18 d.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18130113-96-victim877" type="victimName">
                     James 
                     Schofield
