                     <interp inst="t18130113-96-person880" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . Stanton brought these things into the shop. I bought them. I delivered them to the office.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18130113-96-person881">
                  THOMAS 
                  PACE
               <interp inst="t18130113-96-person881" type="surname" value="PACE"></interp>
