            . I am an officer. These are the things that Mr. Stillwel delivered to me.</p>
               <p>Prosecutor. They are mine.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I would wish to go to sea, if they would accept of Plea.</p>
               <p>GUILTY, aged 19.</p>
